To make this work, you need create a symbol link CUnit to real path of CUnit directory.

or install the header and lib to system search dir.

sudo cp -P <CUnit instaled_path>/lib/libcunit.*  /usr/local/lib/
sudo ln -sf <CUnit instaled_path>/include/CUnit/ /usr/local/include/CUnit
sudo ldconfig

Refer to this webpage to install CUnit:
https://blog.csdn.net/benkaoya/article/details/95870801

Here is a Chinese version CUnit manual:
https://blog.csdn.net/benkaoya/article/details/95887879

